'''diff_level''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the pre-defined difficulty levels in the game.<br><br>
0 = easy-mode<br>
1 = normal-mode<br>
2 = hard-mode<br>
3 = custom<br>
You can edit the custom difficulty by changing the values of the [[Main/en/diff custom]] entry.

<pre>
[difficulty]
diff_level = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 ]

'''Default:''' 0


